metadata.name: 555 DAYS
metadata.description:
Daily Renders Curtain is now close.

Everything that I did in this journey since day 1 led me to this point, to DAY #555. A piece about change and transformation that is occuring or about to occur in life. A sign of good luck, encouragement or guidance.

It was a crazy ride, and it's all worth it! This journey taught me a lot of things and I can't wait to create more art and memories with y'all!

So for that, this is for you for being an awesome human being!

I hope you enjoy this piece just like the other ones before it.

-MEJ.
